name: Cathedral Of The Dancing Heavens III
description:
With wings of aurora, singing eternal.

Process: A Sony KV-13FM12, Aiptek IS-DV2, Panasonic WJ-MX50A, Panasonic WJ-MX30 and Videonics MX-1 dreaming of each other, through each other. Direct capture played back through a Sony KV-13FM12 and rescanned via Nikon D7100 donning an Asahi SMC Takumar 1.8/55.
